# AI & LLM Integration — Implementation Plan

## Current State

| What Exists | Details |
|---|---|
| **Insights Engine** | Simple moving average forecast, reorder alerts, spend anomaly (30% threshold), supplier risk |
| **Analytics** | SQL aggregations (spend by category, supplier performance, monthly spend) |
| **AI Dependencies** | None — no ML/LLM libraries installed |
| **API Keys** | None — [.env](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/.env) has no Groq/Gemini keys |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Pre-requisite:** User must get a free Groq API key from [console.groq.com](https://console.groq.com) and add `GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...` to [.env](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/.env). Optional: Gemini API key as backup.

---

## Build Order (5 Waves)

```mermaid
graph LR
    W1["Wave 1\nLLM Foundation\n+ Chat + NL Requests"] --> W2["Wave 2\nML Models\nForecasting + Anomaly"]
    W2 --> W3["Wave 3\nSupplier Scoring\n+ LLM Explanation"]
    W3 --> W4["Wave 4\nDocument AI\nOCR + Email Parsing"]
    W4 --> W5["Wave 5\nInvoice Match\n+ Fraud Detection"]
```

