## Wave 1: LLM Foundation + AI Chat + NL Purchase Requests

**New Dependencies:** `groq`, `google-generativeai` (backup)

---

### LLM Service (Core)

#### [NEW] [llm_service.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/llm_service.py)

Central LLM wrapper with Groq primary + Gemini fallback:
- `async query_llm(prompt, system_prompt, json_mode)` — returns parsed response
- Auto-retries on rate limit, falls back to Gemini
- Token usage tracking

---

### Integration 1: Natural Language Purchase Request

#### [NEW] [ai_router.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/routers/ai.py)

Endpoints:
- `POST /api/ai/parse-request` — NL text → structured PR items with product matching
- `POST /api/ai/chat` — RAG-powered chat (Integration 8)
- `POST /api/ai/explain-supplier` — supplier recommendation explanation

