### Integration 8: AI Chat Assistant (RAG)

#### [NEW] [ai_chat.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/ai_chat.py)

RAG service that:
1. Classifies user intent (spend query, PO status, supplier lookup, etc.)
2. Fetches relevant DB data via SQL queries
3. Sends data + question to LLM for natural language answer

