Floating chat bubble (bottom-right) with:
- Message history, typing indicator
- Suggested questions based on current page
- Links to referenced POs/suppliers in responses

#### [MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/client/src/app/(dashboard)/layout.tsx)

Add `<AIChatWidget />` globally.

