## Wave 2: ML Demand Forecasting + Price Anomaly Detection

**New Dependencies:** `prophet`, `scikit-learn`, `pandas`, `numpy`

---

### Integration 2: Prophet Demand Forecasting

#### [MODIFY] [insights_engine.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/insights_engine.py)

Replace [generate_forecast()](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/insights_engine.py#182-236) (simple moving avg) with Prophet:
- Per-product forecasting with yearly seasonality
- 90-day predictions with confidence intervals
- Automatic reorder date calculation

#### [NEW] [forecast_service.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/forecast_service.py)

- `forecast_product(product_id, db)` — trains Prophet on PO history
- `forecast_all(db)` — batch forecast for all active products
- `calculate_reorder_date(product_id, db)` — when to order based on stock + forecast

#### [MODIFY] AI Insights frontend

Update forecast charts to show confidence intervals (upper/lower bounds).

---

### Integration 6: Price Anomaly Detection

#### [NEW] [anomaly_service.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/anomaly_service.py)

IsolationForest-based price monitoring:
- `detect_price_anomaly(product_id, new_price, db)` — returns anomaly flag + deviation %
- `batch_check_prices(db)` — scans all recent prices
- Hooks into supplier price update/creation endpoints

#### [MODIFY] [supplier_prices.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/routers/supplier_prices.py)

Add anomaly check on price create/update — returns warning if anomalous.

---

## Wave 3: Smart Supplier Scoring + LLM Explanation

---

### Integration 7: Supplier Recommendation

#### [NEW] [supplier_scorer.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/supplier_scorer.py)

Weighted scoring algorithm:
- Price competitiveness (30%): vs market average
- Delivery reliability (30%): on-time rate from PO history
- Quality rating (25%): existing DB rating
- Response time (15%): average lead time
- `score_supplier(supplier_id, product_id, db)` → composite score 0-10
- `rank_suppliers_for_product(product_id, db)` → sorted list with scores

#### [MODIFY] [ai_router.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/routers/ai.py)

`POST /api/ai/explain-supplier` — takes ML scores → LLM writes human explanation.

#### [MODIFY] Supplier pages

Show scorecard on supplier detail with radar chart (price/delivery/quality/response).

---

## Wave 4: Document AI (OCR + Email Parsing)

**New Dependencies:** `pytesseract`, `Pillow`, `python-multipart`, `PyPDF2`

---

### Integration 3: Price Sheet OCR

#### [NEW] [ocr_service.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/ocr_service.py)

- `extract_text_from_pdf(file)` — PDF → raw text (Tesseract + PyPDF2)
- `extract_text_from_image(file)` — image → raw text
- `parse_price_sheet(raw_text, product_catalog)` — LLM extracts structured prices

#### [NEW] [documents.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/routers/documents.py)

- `POST /api/documents/upload-price-sheet` — upload + OCR + LLM parse
- `POST /api/documents/confirm-prices` — human confirms → updates supplier prices
- Returns extracted items with confidence scores for review

### Integration 5: Supplier Email Parsing

#### [MODIFY] [ai_router.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/routers/ai.py)

- `POST /api/ai/parse-email` — raw email text → structured quote data
- Matches products to catalog, extracts prices/terms/availability

