## Wave 5: Invoice Matching + Fraud Detection

---

### Integration 9: Invoice 3-Way Matching

#### [NEW] [invoice_service.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/invoice_service.py)

- `match_invoice_to_po(invoice_data, po_id, db)` — PO vs delivery vs invoice
- Returns: match status, discrepancies, recommended action
- OCR integration for scanned invoices

### Integration 10: Spend Anomaly & Fraud Detection

#### [NEW] [fraud_detection.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/fraud_detection.py)

Pattern detectors:
- **Split orders**: same user, same supplier, amounts below approval limit
- **New supplier + large order**: first order exceeds threshold
- **Off-hours activity**: POs approved on weekends/nights
- **Unusual spending**: department spends 0 for months then large spike
- `scan_for_fraud(db)` → list of flagged patterns with severity

#### [MODIFY] [insights_engine.py](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/insights_engine.py)

Add fraud alerts to [generate_insights()](file:///Users/commerciax/Desktop/AI_Procurement_sys/server/app/services/insights_engine.py#16-29).

