## Verification Plan

### Per-Wave Testing
| Wave | Test |
|---|---|
| 1 | Chat with assistant, parse NL purchase request, verify structured output |
| 2 | Compare Prophet forecast vs simple avg, test anomaly on extreme price |
| 3 | Score known suppliers, verify ranking matches expectations |
| 4 | Upload sample PDF price sheet, verify extracted items |
| 5 | Create mismatched invoice, verify 3-way match flags it |

### Swagger UI
All new endpoints testable at `http://localhost:8000/docs`
